{"tid":990312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018明星網絡熱度排行榜出爐　女星迪麗熱巴稱冠","createTime":"2019-01-21T12:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T18:50:45.000Z","uid":174420,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3215e83912afdf12fe4b167f435a685987e9fff","tid":990312,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2342307/org/5b56d386e810956ec65348e07b679234.jpg/unWCIwp5sK-N9FTM0--VyY76oAxmjNNLag5RTWoOUU0?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2342307%2Forg%2F5b56d386e810956ec65348e07b679234.jpg%2FunWCIwp5sK-N9FTM0--VyY76oAxmjNNLag5RTWoOUU0%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=371bf76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018女明星網絡熱度排行TOP10，排名先後次序分別是：迪麗熱巴、楊冪、趙麗穎、吳宣儀、楊超越、孟美岐、楊紫、宋茜、范冰冰、鄭爽。迪麗熱巴絕對是大熱登上榜首、楊冪和趙麗穎分別居於亞軍和季軍位置亦屬意料之內，反而內地演藝界一姐范冰冰只得第9位，未知是否與她的逃稅風波有關<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2342321/org/13fc4841ab9466934b426e1c11267151.jpg/vBJP1FRcfsiiaoR9edUZi8MtDY4ITw_TT52Z4E-dmeA?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2342321%2Forg%2F13fc4841ab9466934b426e1c11267151.jpg%2FvBJP1FRcfsiiaoR9edUZi8MtDY4ITw_TT52Z4E-dmeA%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=63d69dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2342331/org/66afb527df59f599d3e8014e6bb572d3.jpg/G_SWtFbk0ZcpPZZqlnBMYHEkBcWDG5LObTiykm04spI?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2342331%2Forg%2F66afb527df59f599d3e8014e6bb572d3.jpg%2FG_SWtFbk0ZcpPZZqlnBMYHEkBcWDG5LObTiykm04spI%3Fv%3Dw480&h=2e575cd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0b3967443db417ac3a481049376d7df1c17b1b1","tid":990312,"uid":36238,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"無人想知支那明星熱唔熱"},{"pid":"ab795542f55c11460af880444377d4ed4e8f1bc3","tid":990312,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco